      <h2>What does a lead generation funnel look like in practice?</h2>

<p>The most common lead generation flow operates in four sequential stages: Attract, Capture, Qualify, and Nurture. Together they form what practitioners call the lead generation funnel — wide at the top where awareness lives, narrow at the bottom where buyers emerge.</p>

